  "subject": "1.15.6 release",
  "commit_message": "1.15.6 release\n\n- update vulnerable dependencies\n  - apache cxf (3.4.1 -> 3.4.10)\n  - logback, org.json, commons-fileupload, kafka-clients,\n    commons-io, h2, swagger-jaxrs2, swagger-parser\n- consistently statically register jackson ObjectMappers on class\n  level for better performance\n- fix plugin related issues that showed up as IDE warnings\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4202\nChange-Id: I75a2a755515a7595222c3a99369c512fa1bec576\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <Fiete.Ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
